<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Devocional</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset básico */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #fafafa;
      color: #333;
      padding: 2rem;
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: auto;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    h1 {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: #34495e;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    h3 {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #555;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
      color: #555;
    }

    .buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .button {
      background-color: #2c3e50;
      color: white;
      padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      box-shadow: 0 3px 6px rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.3);
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .button:hover {
      background-color: #1a2733;
    }

    iframe {
      width: 100%;
      height: 315px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
      h2 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }
      iframe {
        height: 200px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Blog</h1>
  <h2>Diario</h2>
  <h3>Reflexión del día</h3>

  <p>
    Este es un resumen del video. Aquí puedes poner los puntos más importantes, una reflexión corta o versículos relacionados.
  </p>

  <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/TU_VIDEO_AQUI" title="Video Devocional" allowfullscreen></iframe>

  <h3>Síguenos en redes:</h3>
  <div class="buttons">
    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/" target="_blank" class="button">Instagram</a>
    <a href="https://www.facebook.com/" target="_blank" class="button">Facebook</a>
    <a href="https://www.youtube.com/" target="_blank" class="button">YouTube</a>
    <a href="https://www.whatsapp.com/" target="_blank" class="button">WhatsApp</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
